I've heard that Superbia's machine technology
is advanced, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300012_02_msg0002
rows.name:
With that technology, the repairs on
Goldmund should be finished in no time, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300012_02_msg0003
rows.name: It would surely be hundreds of times faster than Tondon, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300012_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, but then Tondon would be
out of a job, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300012_02_msg0005
rows.name: That would be a problem, so no thank you, mo!
